</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Nightmare Bow-correct me if i am wrong but..</span><hr size=1> I have all the components to make it--just not the skill.<br>
So I do An ooc to see who has a skill of 250 in fletching.<br>
I get an answer &quot;what do you need to combine&quot;.  I then ask him if he were to mind if he combines it for me.  He then said he will on one condition--the first combine is his and the next would be mine--WTF--It took me long enough to get these components, and now he wants to make 5k off of me by taking them if i had duplicate ones???<br>
<br>
I mean I am just asking for 5 minutes of his time, nothing else--i would have even paid 1k for the combine but i didnt get that far cuz i was kinda pissed that he wouldnt do the combine, unless i gave him the stuff for it.  Was i WRONG in assuming that a NICE persone woulda had said sure and done it--I mean i know it took him X number of days and X number of pp to get his skill to 250, but really<br>
he coulda asked for a certain amount for just the combine itself and i woulda gladly paid....<br>
<br>
Please post your thoughts...Thanks<br>
