You have got to be kidding right? Lythe nailed it, JC is 100% a vendor bought skill and 250 can be gotten for under 5k plats. Platinum jade rings (trivial &gt;250) cost 108pp per attempt and sell back to the vendor for around 103pp each. If you stay near your trivial when you work on JC you will succeed on 90%+ of your attempts. If you have a chanter friend you can actually profit from your skill ups since imbued jewelry sells back to a vendor for a profit.<br>
<br>
Comparing JC to any other trade skill is like comparing getting a rogue epic to getting a backpack full of green scales.<br>
